# Obsidian Vault (ops/raspberry-pi/obsidian-vault)

Vault lives on OneDrive, **outside** this repo. Daily notes: `Diary/`. Skill: `.cursor/skills/obsidian-vault/SKILL.md`.

## Paths

| Environment | Vault | Git metadata |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Windows | `C:\Users\Ben\OneDrive\Obsidian\hej` | `%USERPROFILE%\.obsidian-vault-backup\vault.git` |
| Raspberry Pi | `/home/ben/obsidian/vault` | `/home/ben/obsidian/backup-git/vault.git` |

Local config (gitignored): `ops/raspberry-pi/obsidian-vault/config.env` — copy from `config.example.env`.

Pi sync/backup runbook: `ops/raspberry-pi/docs/obsidian-vault-backup.md`.

## Scripts

| Script | Use for |
| --- | --- |
| `vault-git-bootstrap.ps1` | One-time Windows git mirror setup |
| `vault-git-snapshot.ps1` | Commit before/after vault edits (`-Push` optional) |
| `analyze-diary-headers.py` | Read-only Diary header/scaffold scan |
| `fix-diary-nav.py` | Fix wrong dates on existing nav lines only (never adds lines) |

## Git safety

Always run `vault-git-snapshot.ps1` **before and after** any vault file mutation from Cursor. Never add `.git` inside the OneDrive vault folder.

## Agent conventions

Read `obsidian-vault/docs/working-in-the-diary.md` before editing Diary notes.

## Analysis output

Reports go to `obsidian-vault/reports/` (gitignored). Committed taxonomy summary: `obsidian-vault/docs/analysis-taxonomy.md`.
